OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,FIrish Premier Micheal Martin is to
OL,7,Fdiscuss the conflict in the Middle
OL,8,FEast with Spanish Prime Minister Pedro
OL,9,FSanchez in Madrid on Tuesday.
OL,11,FMr Sanchez has emerged as the EU's
OL,12,Fmost vocal critic of a bombing
OL,13,Fcampaign by the US and Israel on Iran,
OL,14,Fcalling it a "violation of
OL,15,Finternational law".
OL,17,FHe has come under pressure from US
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump as a result,
OL,19,Fwho threatened to "cut off all trade
OL,20,Fwith Spain".
OL,26,@vD@NOUwD@RO]{D@SOU|D@KO]
