CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773122647
OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,FThe Irish Government has said that
OL,7,Fwhile the US-Israeli military
OL,8,Foffensive on Iran took place without a
OL,9,FUN mandate, it stopped short of saying
OL,10,Fthat it contravened international law.
OL,12,FMr Martin's meeting with Mr Sanchez
OL,13,Fcomes a week before the Irish Premier
OL,14,Fmeets Mr Trump in the Oval Office on
OL,15,FSt Patrick's Day.
OL,17,FMr Martin's trip to Madrid is part of
OL,18,Fseveral to EU capitals ahead of
OL,19,FIreland taking up the EU presidency
OL,20,Ffor six months from July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
