CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773122647
OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,FThe leaders are expected to discuss
OL,7,Fthe agenda for the presidency, as well
OL,8,Fas "excellent" relations between the
OL,9,Ftwo countries.
OL,11,FMr Martin said he was looking forward
OL,12,Fto meeting Mr Sanchez in the Spanish
OL,13,Fcapital.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773122647
OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,F"The success of our presidency will
OL,7,Frely on the goodwill of our EU
OL,8,Fpartners, and therefore it is
OL,9,Fimportant that I hear from my fellow
OL,10,FEU leaders on what their priorities
OL,11,Fand concerns are on the range of
OL,12,Fissues that Ireland will be seeking to
OL,13,Fprogress during the six months of our
OL,14,Fpresidency," Mr Martin said ahead of
OL,15,Fthe meeting.
OL,17,F"Improving Europe's competitiveness,
OL,18,Fenhancing our security, and promoting
OL,19,Fand protecting our shared values will
OL,20,Fbe the priority issues for our
OL,21,Fpresidency.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773122647
OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,F"Across these areas, there are many
OL,7,Fdetailed and complex files which we
OL,8,Fwill be tasked with advancing, not
OL,9,Fleast the EU's next multiannual budget.
OL,11,F"I will also discuss global issues
OL,12,Fwith Prime Minister Sanchez, including
OL,13,Fthe serious situations in the Middle
OL,14,FEast and Ukraine.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773122647
OL,3,CIrish Premier to meet Spanish leader
OL,4,CSanchez in Madrid
OL,6,F"Ireland and Spain share excellent
OL,7,Fbilateral relations, built on strong
OL,8,Fhistorical links and close cultural
OL,9,Faffinity, and I look forward to
OL,10,Fdiscussing how we can work together to
OL,11,Ffurther strengthen cooperation on
OL,12,Ftrade, investment, energy, education,
OL,13,Fresearch and culture."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
